《'''寻找薇薇安·迈尔'''》（{{lang-en|Finding Vivian Maier}}）是一部关于摄影师[[薇薇安·迈尔|薇薇安·迈尔]]的2013年[[纪录片|纪录片]]，约翰·马鲁夫（John Maloof）和查理·西斯科尔（Charlie Siskel）[[编剧|编剧]]、[[导演|导演]]兼[[制片|制片]]<ref>"[http://variety.com/2014/film/news/finding-vivian-maier-reveals-life-of-mysterious-street-photographer-1201145184/ ‘Finding Vivian Maier’ Reveals Life of Mysterious Street Photographer] {{Wayback|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/finding-vivian-maier-reveals-life-of-mysterious-street-photographer-1201145184/ |date=20200813095823 }}", [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety (magazine)]]. Accessed 7 August 2014.</ref><ref>"[http://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2014/03/31/candid-camera-2 Candid Camera] {{Wayback|url=http://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2014/03/31/candid-camera-2 |date=20201124132702 }}", [[The_New_Yorker|The New Yorker]]. Accessed 7 August 2014.</ref><ref>"[http://www.villagevoice.com/2014-03-26/film/finding-vivian-maier-documentary/ Finding Vivian Maier Is a Fascinating Tale of the Street Photographer] {{Wayback|url=http://www.villagevoice.com/2014-03-26/film/finding-vivian-maier-documentary/ |date=20140804131738 }}", The Village Voice. Accessed 7 August 2014.</ref><ref>"[http://online.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424052702303725404579461170488341910 Nanny Strangest: On "Finding Vivian Maier"] {{Wayback|url=http://online.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424052702303725404579461170488341910 |date=20140810041120 }}", [[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]]. Accessed 7 August 2014.</ref><ref>"[http://nypost.com/2014/03/22/recluse-nanny-turns-out-to-be-photography-genius/ Recluse nanny turns out to be photography genius] {{Wayback|url=http://nypost.com/2014/03/22/recluse-nanny-turns-out-to-be-photography-genius/ |date=20201111195631 }}", [[New_York_Post|New York Post]]. Accessed 7 August 2014.</ref><ref>"[http://www.nytimes.com/2014/03/23/movies/a-documentary-looks-at-the-photographer-vivian-maier.html?action=click&module=Search&region=searchResults%230&version=&url=http%3A%2F%2Fquery.nytimes.com%2Fsearch%2Fsitesearch%2F%3Faction%3Dclick%26region%3DMasthead%26pgtype%3DHomepage%26module%3DSearchSubmit%26contentCollection%3DHomepage%26t%3Dqry156%23%2Ffinding%2Bvivian%2Bmaier%2Fsince1851%2Fallresults%2F1%2Fallauthors%2Fnewest%2F&_r=1 A Mystery Woman’s Eye on the World: A Documentary Looks at the Photographer Vivian Maier] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/03/23/movies/a-documentary-looks-at-the-photographer-vivian-maier.html?action=click&module=Search&region=searchResults%230&version=&url=http%3A%2F%2Fquery.nytimes.com%2Fsearch%2Fsitesearch%2F%3Faction%3Dclick%26region%3DMasthead%26pgtype%3DHomepage%26module%3DSearchSubmit%26contentCollection%3DHomepage%26t%3Dqry156%23%2Ffinding%2Bvivian%2Bmaier%2Fsince1851%2Fallresults%2F1%2Fallauthors%2Fnewest%2F&_r=1 |date=20150220212933 }}", [[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]. Accessed 7 August 2014.</ref>。迈尔穷尽毕生留下摄影遗产却鲜有人知。电影记录了马鲁夫发现她的作品的过程，并在她过世后，通过采访认识她的人，发现她是一位[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]的保姆兼摄影师。

电影2013年9月9日于[[2013年多伦多国际电影节|2013年多伦多国际电影节]]首映，2014年11月发布DVD<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/nov/15/finding-vivian-maier-review | date = 19 November 2014 | accessdate = 6 February 2015 | first = Charlie | last = Lyne | newspaper = [[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] | title = Finding Vivian Maier out now on DVD | archive-date = 2018-02-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180213003542/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/nov/15/finding-vivian-maier-review | dead-url = no }}</ref>，荣获各种奖项，获得[[第68届英国电影学院奖|第68届英国电影学院奖]]最佳纪录片奖和[[第87届奥斯卡金像奖|第87届奥斯卡金像奖]][[奥斯卡最佳纪录片奖|最佳纪录片奖]]提名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.out.com/entertainment/popnography/2015/01/15/lgbt-oscar-nominations-imitation-game-meryl-streep-still-alice-|title=2015 Oscar Nominations: Imitation Game, Meryl Streep, Still Alice & More|work=Out Magazine|access-date=2015-02-11|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117014017/http://www.out.com/entertainment/popnography/2015/01/15/lgbt-oscar-nominations-imitation-game-meryl-streep-still-alice-|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

